2011-10-03T23:45:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/taiwan-daybook-inflationary-pressure-eases-formosa-earnings.html
(Corrects to say Formosa Petrochemicals reported loss in
Equity Movers.)  Global inflationary pressure is
easing as the world economic recovery slows,  Taiwan ’s central
bank said in a report released yesterday that Governor Perng Fai-nan will present to Parliament on Oct. 5.  The four biggest units of Formosa Plastics Group, Taiwan’s
largest diversified company, posted third-quarter pretax
earnings that missed analyst estimates after accidents reduced
output.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  